ZH: 只有通过努力才能取得成功。
EN: Only through hard work can we achieve success.

ZH: 只要你努力学习，一定能通过考试。
EN: As long as you study hard, you will definitely pass the exam.

ZH: 只有一个人通过了面试。
EN: Only one person passed the interview.

ZH: 只有我一个人喜欢吃辣的食物。
EN: I am the only one who likes spicy food.

ZH: 只有适合的人才能胜任这个职位。
EN: Only the suitable person can handle this position.

ZH: 你只需等待一会儿。
EN: You only need to wait for a moment.

ZH: 只有那家店有我要的东西。
EN: Only that store has what I need.

ZH: 她只在周末去购物。
EN: She only goes shopping on weekends.

ZH: 等我完成任务，就可以休息了。
EN: Only when I finish the task can I rest.

ZH: 在这里只能停留半小时。
EN: You can only stay here for half an hour.

ZH: 他只能忍受这种疼痛。
EN: He can only endure this kind of pain.

ZH: 只有十个人能进入下一轮比赛。
EN: Only ten people can enter the next round of the competition.

ZH: 他只有一个朋友。
EN: He only has one friend.

ZH: 只要你来参加，我们就会举办聚会。
EN: We will hold a party only if you come to attend.

ZH: 你只需要做好准备就可以面对任何挑战。
EN: You only need to be prepared to face any challenge.

ZH: 我们只剩下最后一件货物。
EN: We only have the last item left.

ZH: 只有全队努力协作，才能取得胜利。
EN: Only when the whole team cooperates can we achieve victory.

ZH: 她只能被她所爱的人所救。
EN: She can only be saved by the person she loves.

ZH: 我们只有一小时时间准备演讲。
EN: We only have one hour to prepare for the speech.

ZH: 这里只允许买一瓶饮料。
EN: Only one bottle of drink is allowed to be purchased here.
